<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/283> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #283" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Liv. 3.65.2; Diod. 12.27.1; Dion. Hal. 11.51.1; Fast. Fer. Lat. ([- - - -Herm]ini[o]), Degrassi 146f., 156; Chr. 354 (Coritinesano et Tricosto); Fast. Hyd. (Hermenio et Tricosto); Chr. Pasc. ({Gr}); Cassiod.; Degrassi 95, 366f." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/282> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #282" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/4> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Herminius' praenomen is Sp. in Livy, but L. in Cassiod., while Diod. has {Gr} and Dion. Hal. {Gr.}. Verginius' cognomen, according to Livy, is Caelimontanus (see Fast. Cap. on 456), while Diod. gives his name variously as {Gr} or {Gr}. The notice in Auct. De Praenom. (4) is \"Consul Lar Herminius cum T. Verginio Costo.\" Degrassi prints Herminius' cognomen as Corinitesano (366f.)." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertion/361> rdfs:label "Post Assertion: #361" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertion ;
